{"tid":1572080,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我已經搵到屬於香港人既勝利法！！！","createTime":"2019-09-15T14:54:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T17:30:06.000Z","uid":154299,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b60392a084110f510a24f9006105d9067939afc1","tid":1572080,"uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:54:37.000Z","msg":"首先好似隔離post巴打咁講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">恭喜香港人再次突破樽頸位</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日見到落單廢老比人打真係好心涼<br />\n我地要話比全世界聽<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">先撩者賤</span></span><br />\n<br />\nPopo已經唔可信<br />\n有事只可以靠自己<br />\n有黑社會 廢老 藍絲 福建幫 乜都好<br />\n<br />\n今日講幾個勝利法比大家聽<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 人數就係一切</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">十則圍之，五則攻之，倍則分之；敵則能戰之，少則能守之，不若則能避之。故小敵之堅，大敵之擒也。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n夠人當然要打柒佢<br />\n<br />\n最好打到佢失去還手嘅能力<br />\n久而久之 俾人打多幾次<br />\n佢就會覺得自己作為藍絲<br />\n生出來就係要俾你打嘅<br />\n打到佢哋懷疑人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2. 不要屌 試著引導</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔認同巴打私了既你<br />\n寧願你走 都唔好做阻膠<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不要說：唔好打 唔好變成對家一樣<br />\n試著說：不完美 可接受</span></span><br />\n然後開遮幫手cover<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nExample: 我面對和理非朋友<br />\n佢地一開始聽到我跳閘都好抵拒<br />\n又話成本高 比人拉 會犯法<br />\n用人服務就要比錢<br />\n不要屌佢地on9<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">試著解釋+教佢地點樣做會容易d<br />\n捐/跟/廢老卡<br />\n佢地就會慢慢突破心理關口</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 勿忘初衷</span></span><br />\n<br />\n記得我地既目標<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最近好多唱歌團 跳閘團 <br />\n好多支線活動<br />\n但係要把持一個中指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">廢老on9 <br />\nPopo濫權<br />\n黑社會賤格<br />\n呢一切一切<br />\n只要落實五大訴求<br />\n就會迎刃而解！！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n目標清晰<br />\n除此之外 一切都係手段！！！<br />\n用一切手段去達到目標<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各有各做！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db93ee3f58b82998595cbe4bd81cfbdfdb1318b4","tid":1572080,"uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:55:00.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"4e2b1f1d7b0508106037a6f62863ae772092e07f","tid":1572080,"uid":154299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:55:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z07oYHJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ07oYHJ.png&h=e1ed2f22&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/di2oYHK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdi2oYHK.png&h=5bb67401&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要改變思考模式<br />\n唔好互相指責 試着引導對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a6031e6fd7b93021c8788f433b7e1e4baca082","tid":1572080,"uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:55:36.000Z","msg":"第3次 轉頭再推"},{"pid":"a713bba9c6d849bc1f4b5a491312b99f900d2469","tid":1572080,"uid":154299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:56:14.000Z","msg":"再黎 推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ba81d94ad9a5c6f86abc46f33e20995003a4aba","tid":1572080,"uid":78300,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:42